Copyright (c) 2026 Seamus Waldron / Hydrate.

The compiled binaries distributed via this repository are licensed,
not sold. Use of the binaries is permitted on machines under your
control for personal or commercial development, subject to the
edition (Free / Pro / Team / Enterprise) you have activated.

You may NOT:

  - redistribute the binaries to third parties;
  - reverse-engineer, decompile, or disassemble the binaries;
  - circumvent licence-activation, telemetry, or rate-limit checks
    built into the binaries;
  - claim authorship of, or derive products from, the binaries.

You MAY:

  - install and run the binaries on your own machines;
  - integrate Hydrate with first- and third-party tools via the
    documented MCP, HTTP, and slash-command surfaces;
  - share configuration files, slash-command templates, and pack
    (`.hpack`) exports you have created.

For commercial licensing, source access enquiries, or terms that
fall outside the above, email `licences@gethydrate.dev`.

THE BINARIES ARE PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND,
EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO THE WARRANTIES OF
MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND
NONINFRINGEMENT. THE FULL EULA SHIPPED INSIDE EACH RELEASE TARBALL
IS THE AUTHORITATIVE TEXT; THIS FILE IS A SUMMARY FOR THE PUBLIC
DISTRIBUTION REPO ONLY.
